---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Key Technologies | Heat & Glo Engineering" description="The Heat & Glo engineering technologies behind every product: IPI ignition systems, direct-vent design, glass cooling, EPA-certified wood combustion, and more." noIndex={true}>
  <main class="max-w-page mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <p class="uppercase tracking-wide text-sm text-orange-700 font-semibold">Key Technologies</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2">The engineering you don't see.</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-700 max-w-2xl">Heat & Glo's product reliability comes from the engineering platforms shared across the lineup. Here are the systems that make the fireplaces work the way they do.</p>
    </header>
    <section class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-5"><p class="font-semibold mb-2">IPI (Intermittent Pilot Ignition)</p><p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">No standing pilot light. The ignition system fires only when the fireplace is in use, saving gas and extending component life.</p></div>
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-5"><p class="font-semibold mb-2">Direct-vent design</p><p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Sealed firebox, co-axial vent pipe, no chimney required. Combustion air drawn from outside; exhaust routed back outside without compromising indoor air quality.</p></div>
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-5"><p class="font-semibold mb-2">Cool-glass technology</p><p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Engineered air-flow patterns reduce front-glass surface temperatures while maintaining radiant performance.</p></div>
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-5"><p class="font-semibold mb-2">EPA-certified wood combustion</p><p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Wood-burning units engineered to meet EPA emissions standards. Listed efficiency ratings on every model.</p></div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
